### ScrimFinder Manual API Tests
@baseUrl = http://34.159.128.218/api/v1
@matchmakingUrl = {{baseUrl}}/matchmaking
@rankingUrl = {{baseUrl}}/ranking
@historyUrl = {{baseUrl}}/history

@queueId = 33e4ab83-5dde-4bb3-9113-53725c799a60
@playerId = 480f88c1-7246-5cd4-9d5a-3561a9b85e64
@riotMatchId = EUW1_7824036381

### 1. Create a Matchmaking Queue
# NOTE: This now automatically syncs with the Ranking Service
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/queues/{{queueId}}
    ?name=Manual E2E Queue
    &requiredPlayers=10
    &region=EUW
    &mode=NORMAL

### 2. Create a Player Profile
# Registers the user in both Matchmaking and Ranking DBs
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/players
    ?id={{playerId}}
    &username=manual_test_user

### 3. Link LoL Account to Player
# Links the internal ID to a real Riot account
POST {{rankingUrl}}/players/{{playerId}}/link
    ?gameName=Simoes88
    &tagLine=nr1
    &region=EUW

### 4. Initialize MMR for the Queue
# CRITICAL: Ranking Service needs a record for this specific queue before joining
POST {{rankingUrl}}/players/{{playerId}}/mmr
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "queueId": "{{queueId}}"
}

### 5. Join Queue
# @name joinQueue
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
    "queueId": "{{queueId}}"
}

### 6. Check Lobby Status (Poll until matched)
# Use the 'matchId' field from the response to proceed
GET {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/{{joinQueue.response.body.id}}/lobby

### 7. Accept the Match
# Replace YOUR_MATCH_UUID with the matchId returned in Step 6
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/YOUR_MATCH_UUID/accept
    ?playerId={{playerId}}

### 8. Link Match to Riot ID (External ID)
# Replace YOUR_MATCH_UUID with the matchId from Step 6
PUT {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/YOUR_MATCH_UUID/link
    ?externalGameId={{riotMatchId}}

### 9. Complete Match
# This triggers the gRPC pipeline to Ranking -> History
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/YOUR_MATCH_UUID/complete

### 10. Verify MMR Update
GET {{rankingUrl}}/players/{{playerId}}/queue?queueId={{queueId}}

### 11. Verify in Match History Service
GET {{historyUrl}}/matches/{{riotMatchId}}
